#MOVIE THEATER create an application that allows a user to buy movie tickets from the theater

#Core Deliverables

    A user should see the first movie details when the page loads. i.e. the poster,showtime,runtime.The number of available tickets will need to be derived by subtracting the number of tickets_sold from the theater's capacity

    See a list of all the movies on the left side of the page.

    A user should be able to buy tickets for a movie. if there are no more tickets the user should see that the movie is sold out.
